Controls:
    Gamepad 1:
        left_bumper & a, b, x, y: Test motors
            a:
            b:
            x:
            y:

        left_stick_x, y: Move robot (field-orientated)
        right_stick_x: Rotate robot
        left_stick_button / right_bumper: Sprint

        right_trigger: Intake IN
        left_trigger: Intake OUT

        back: Reset IMU

    Gamepad 2:
        a: Arm load position
        b / x: Arm carry position
        y: Arm delivery position
        right_stick_y: Manually set arm position

        right_trigger: Fully open bucket door (while arm is in delivery position)
        left_trigger: Halfway open bucket door (while arm is in delivery position)

        right_bumper: Launch drone